body:
UVM tests/20sequences/90Mantis/4488_forgot_wait_for_relevant fails post-$final because the do...while loops that are part of V3Sched's IterCounts do not check for hitting a finish.  See also #7213.

Fix coming soon hopefully.

Example:

```
module t;
  int cyc;
  event e;
  always @ (e) begin
    $display("e=%0d", e);
    ->e;
    cyc = cyc + 1;
    if (cyc >= 10) begin
      $display("Fin");
      $finish;
    end
  end
  initial begin
    #1;
    ->e;
    #1;
  end
  final begin
    if (cyc != 10) $stop;
  end
endmodule
```

